Before Me, the undersigned Notary Public, personally came and appeared Sean Galley, the duly authorized agent of US
Roofing Systems, LLC for the purposes of only signing and presenting for filing this Claim of Lien, who was duly sworn
and says that, pursuant to the information provided by US Roofing Systems, LLC the information on this Claim of Lien is
accurate and true. And, solely as represented by US Roofing Systems, LLC through information provided, that in
accordance with a contract with the Hiring Party, the Lienor Furnished the labor, services, and/or materials above-
identified as the Services, said Services were furnished on the above-described Property,
The Property is owned by the Property Owner.
As represented by US Roofing Systems, LLC the total contract price between the Hiring Party and the Lienor is above-
identified as the Amount of Total Contract. Of this amount, the above-identified Amount of Total Claim remains unpaid, the
Services were first furnished to the Property on the above-identified Dates Services First Furnished, and last furnished to
the Property on the above-identified Dates Services Last Furnished, and the Lienor delivered the required preliminary
Notice to Owner on the above-indicated dates to the above-indicated parties, if any.
Signed:
-
US Roofing Systems, LLC, Lienor
Signed by: Sean Galley agent
Date: May 31, 2022
Sworn to (or affirmed) and subscribed before me, Notary Public, on May 31, 2022
(SEAL)
